   <head>¶ To the Christian Rea<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>der.</head>
   <p>Least any man shoulde be of<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>fended with the reading of these thinges which are here written, Beza testifieth that he will be rea<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>die to conferre Christianly with any concerning the same, &amp; geue place too those who shall teache more certayne thinges out of the worde of God.</p>
